Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}自分だけのSTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:15.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}'Cause we're still ROUGH DIAMONDS on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:17.84,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着比心中描繪的圖景更遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:27.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}一步一步前進 真實還很遙遠 旅途漫漫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:32.94,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}將彼此的自尊磨個透亮吧
