Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.82,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}就不用去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:44.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}互相碰撞 不斷磨練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)\an8}Rolling Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.00,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}相遇就是SHOCKWAVE！SHOCKWAVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.83,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.00,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}開始前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.50,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}無謀的挑戰者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}就用手中的刀刃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}去開拓明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}不是任何其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.81,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:15.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}{\an8}'Cause we're still ROUGH DIAMONDS on the road!
